<lb n="0215a03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0215001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】三十帖策子第十七，【乙】黃檗版淨嚴等加筆本</note><title>毘沙門天王經</title></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0215a04"/>
<lb n="0215a05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0215002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（（開府…師））三十九字＝（（特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智））十七字【宋】【元】，（（唐特進試鴻臚卿三藏沙門大廣智））十四字【明】【乙】，（（大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智））十一字【甲】</note><app n="0215002" word-count="39"><lem>開府儀同三司特進試鴻臚卿肅
<lb n="0215a06"/>國公食邑三千戶贈司空諡大鑒
<lb n="0215a07"/>正號大廣智大興善寺三藏法師</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】" resp="Taisho">特進試鴻臚卿大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">唐特進試鴻臚卿三藏沙門大廣智</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">大興善寺三藏沙門大廣智</rdg></app>
<lb n="0215a08"/>不空奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0215a09"/><p>爾時毘沙門天王。在於佛前合掌。白佛言世
<lb n="0215a10"/>尊。我為未來諸有情等利益安樂。豐饒財寶
<lb n="0215a11"/>護持國界故。說自真言。<note n="0215003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔我此真言〕－【甲】</note><app n="0215003"><lem>我此真言</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。如真多摩
<lb n="0215a12"/>尼寶<note n="0215004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">王＝心【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0215004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">王＝心【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0215004"><lem>王</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>能滿眾願。世尊聽許我說。佛言善哉
<lb n="0215a13"/>善哉天王。汝能愍念為諸有情。恣汝意說</p>
<lb n="0215a14"/><p>爾時毘沙門天王歡喜無量即於佛前說心真
<lb n="0215a15"/>言曰</p>
<lb n="0215a16"/><p type="dharani"><note n="0215005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">梵字真言附載於卷末</note>曩謨囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>怛囉<note place="inline">二合</note>夜<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">一</note>曩謨吠室
<lb n="0215a17"/>囉<note place="inline">二合</note><note n="0215006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">麼＝摩【三】【乙】＊</note><note n="0215006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">麼＝摩【宋】【元】【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0215006"><lem>麼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">摩</rdg></app>拏<note place="inline">鼻<note n="0215007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＝音【甲】＊</note><app n="0215007"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">音</rdg></app></note>野<note place="inline">二</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>囉<note place="inline">引</note>惹<note place="inline">引</note>野<note place="inline">三</note>薩
