<lb n="0215b03"/><p>爾時毘沙門天王說此真言已。白佛言世尊。
<lb n="0215b04"/>我今<note n="0215027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（當）＋說【乙】</note><app n="0215027"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">當說</rdg></app>受持真言法。先取安<note n="0215028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉＝息【明】【乙】＊</note><app n="0215028"><lem>悉</lem><rdg wit="【明】【乙】" resp="Taisho">息</rdg></app>香白檀香
<lb n="0215b05"/>龍腦香多&CB00754;囉香薰陸香蘇合香。和合此香。
<lb n="0215b06"/>供養我毘沙門天王。若迎請時結根本印。以
<lb n="0215b07"/>二頭指向身三招。即誦真言七遍頂上散印</p>
<lb n="0215b08"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00135;也<note place="inline">二合</note>他<note place="inline">去引一</note>曩謨<note n="0215029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吠引＝引吠【乙】</note><app n="0215029"><lem>吠<note place="inline">引</note></lem><rdg wit="【乙】" resp="Taisho">引吠</rdg></app>室囉<note place="inline">二合</note>麼<note place="inline">鼻<note n="0215030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔音呼〕－【三】【甲】【乙】</note><note n="0215030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔音呼〕－【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】</note><app n="0215030"><lem>音呼</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【甲】【乙】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app></note>
